{"tid":851175,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解任何兩個自然數相加出下個term既列，相鄰數比approach黃金？","createTime":"2018-10-07T02:55:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-07T17:44:24.000Z","uid":165773,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2ad2eeb903a56337f3d502e0ecff4dda4b7cb98a","tid":851175,"uid":165773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T02:55:50.000Z","msg":"a,b,a+b,a+2b,2a+3b,3a+5b,5a+8b...<br />\n個數列開始既a同b<br />\n可以係是但任何正整數<br />\n下一個term既定義係上兩個term相加出來<br />\n原理同fibonacci 數列個生產方法一樣。<br />\n<br />\n用計數機試過發現<br />\n當個數列愈後<br />\n相鄰既terms相除會愈接近1.618...<br />\n黃金比例。<br />\n<br />\n即係話a+b除b<br />\n一定比b除a更接近黃金比例。<br />\n5a+8b除3a+5b一定比<br />\n3a+5b除2a+3b<br />\n更接近黃金比例。<br />\n<br />\n點解會咁？"},{"pid":"7b2654c17773b13d0abcefdb11efd9c3418d9b7b","tid":851175,"uid":87030,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2ad2eeb903a56337f3d502e0ecff4dda4b7cb98a","tid":851175,"uid":165773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T02:55:50.000Z","msg":"a,b,a+b,a+2b,2a+3b,3a+5b,5a+8b...<br />\n個數列開始既a同b<br />\n可以係是但任何正整數<br />\n下一個term既定義係上兩個term相加出來<br />\n原理同fibonacci 數列個生產方法一樣。<br />\n<br />\n用計數機試過發現<br />\n當個數列愈後<br />\n相鄰既terms相除會愈接近1.618...<br />\n黃金比例。<br />\n<br />\n即係話a+b除b<br />\n一定比b除a更接近黃金比例。<br />\n5a+8b除3a+5b一定比<br />\n3a+5b除2a+3b<br />\n更接近黃金比例。<br />\n<br />\n點解會咁？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-07T12:49:19.000Z","msg":"因為黃金比例本身就係係來至fib<br />\n<br />\n黃金比例定義係root: x+1=x^2<br />\n<br />\n然而fib series : A<span style=\"font-size: small;\">n</span>=A<span style=\"font-size: small;\">n-1</span> + A<span style=\"font-size: small;\">n-2</span><br />\n<br />\n然而A<span style=\"font-size: small;\">n</span>/A<span style=\"font-size: small;\">n-1</span>= 1+A<span style=\"font-size: small;\">n-2</span>/A<span style=\"font-size: small;\">n-3</span><br />\n<br />\n如果我地假設當n無限大個陣 ,lim n-&gt; inf An/An-1 =x<br />\n<br />\nThen An-2/An-1 =1/x<br />\n<br />\n你會得到算式x=1+1/x<br />\n<br />\nx^2=x+1<br />\n<br />\n因此會有你既結果"},{"pid":"9